Interface SqlTypeName.PrecScale

  • Enclosing class:
    SqlTypeName

    private static interface SqlTypeName.PrecScale
    Flags indicating precision/scale combinations.

    Note: for intervals:

    • precision = start (leading field) precision
    • scale = fractional second precision
